# Claude Code Instructions

Claude Code loads project memory from `CLAUDE.md` and project skills from `.claude/skills/*/SKILL.md`.

Use the shared repository instructions in @AGENTS.md.

For reusable project workflow guidance, use the project skill in @.claude/skills/skelenest-project/SKILL.md.

## Claude-Specific Notes

- Use the project skill whenever editing modules, auth, persistence, runtime configuration, tests, or selected-stack conventions.
- Keep generated code aligned with the selected Skelenest stack.
- If instructions conflict, follow the user's latest request first, then this file, then shared repository instructions.
